title: Tapped out:Squidport
description:
This works with the current Squidport. Once installed Cletus's farm will give the option to grow money, XP, and donuts instantly.  
Uninstall any version you currently have. Install TSTO_v430_v0 using any file manager. open when done and let it update all the way. DO NOT LOG IN YET, just open when done and back out.  Install TSTO_v430_v2. It will say its' already there and blah blah, just install.  Enjoy
